  "uuid": "3b796fd6e01ed4a19f5a00917db4c2f8",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>We are seeking a highly motivated and creative Senior Marketing Executive to plan, manage, and execute integrated marketing campaigns across retail and digital channels, with a focus on brand awareness, customer engagement, and campaign performance.<br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conceptualise, develop, and execute marketing campaigns to drive brand awareness and customer engagement across retail and digital platforms.</p></li><li><p>Manage an annual marketing plan and marketing calendar, including campaign budgeting, scheduling, and resource planning.</p></li><li><p>Develop, execute, and optimise digital marketing and digital advertising campaigns across platforms such as Google, YouTube, Instagram, and Facebook.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and deliver marketing presentations, proposals, and post-campaign reports to management for review and approval.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with internal stakeholders to ensure alignment and effective campaign execution.</p></li><li><p>Manage relationships with external vendors to ensure quality delivery and cost effectiveness.</p></li><li><p>Analyse campaign performance, track results, and recommend improvements to enhance marketing effectiveness.</p></li><li><p>Delegate tasks and monitor work progress to ensure timely and accurate execution of marketing initiatives.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proven experience in marketing communications, digital marketing, and retail marketing.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience managing paid digital advertising and marketing campaigns across major digital platforms.</p></li><li><p>Strong creative thinking, conceptualisation, and problem-solving skills.</p></li><li><p>Ability to analyse information, make sound decisions, and propose practical solutions and recommendations.</p></li><li><p>Strong project management and budget management skills, with the ability to meet deadlines and work under pressure.</p></li><li><p>Excellent presentation, interpersonal, and written communication skills.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently as well as collaboratively within a team.</p></li><li><p>Experience guiding or supervising team members will be an advantage.</p></li></ul>",
